{"tid":1393621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線要討論有咩步署或行動 以後舉手投票決定","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T07:40:30.000Z","uid":61886,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1054a4d9ae27290c8de081d5549f9005ebdb9fe0","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:10.000Z","msg":"前線資訊好唔流通<br />\n同時有多條戰線<br />\n就算一條戰線 前線都講緊有幾十人<br />\n每次有最新資訊/決定<br />\n要開會討論<br />\n都只係得十個八個圍住傾<br />\n每個人諗法都唔同<br />\n好難達成共識<br />\n最終變成膠著狀態<br />\n<br />\n我建議<br />\n由哨兵/前線用大聲公講資訊/決定<br />\n如果係決定 請連埋解釋<br />\n盡量提供多方面既資訊<br />\n同正反既原因<br />\n<br />\n然後比前線互相用3分鐘討論<br />\n跟住舉手投票<br />\n例如<br />\n留守依條街 定 退守去後一條街<br />\n留守依條街 定 轉場去xxx <br />\n最後少數服從多數<br />\n<br />\n依個方法有幾個好處<br />\n1. 體現民主精神<br />\n2. 用較快既方法做到決定<br />\n3. 減低資訊傳輸既失誤<br />\n<br />\n認同請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489f6f78aae6ea473c89b15acf8e38b87fd1c8f8","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"睇Winter on Fire<br />\n喺廣場 大家都係舉手決定"},{"pid":"14f471b62fb8aaf414d25626e4ddfd543eac3c4d","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:00:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c82be947fb0251f51f77ffebb6cc889fa9cbf6d7","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20e4b007d846f15cec17187a73ffd58b7d5af95","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:03:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"26a27273a47b37be4610641956043ba7547ecb81","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e3ea077a6da68bd7302a83c99854636d9c856c93","tid":1393621,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:10:35.000Z","msg":"前線都玩山頭文化"},{"pid":"685772969eb86588b9770268c9e1b7b95d41ba96","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:30:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f542606e926e9013ea3afecbc09fd1246c90aa1","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:32:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f20b0029d0a89cbf5596dc328852a628452dfe","tid":1393621,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}